\f0\b\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
How do you define digital transformation?
\f1\b0 \'a0Different people define this term in different ways. Generally speaking, digital transformation refers to leveraging digital technology to enhance an organization across different dimensions, such as the IT infrastructure, business processes, and the digital culture. Others include\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.walkme.com/blog/improve-customer-experience/?t=21&camp=adoption-blog"}}{\fldrslt customer experience improvements}}, business strategy, and other business areas.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
What experience and expertise do you offer that can benefit our digital transformation initiatives?
\f1\b0 \'a0Naturally, it is important to focus on one\'92s own IT expertise and leadership abilities. More specifically, it is useful to emphasize how one\'92s own abilities will help the organization achieve its business goals.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
What is your approach to leading digital transformation?
\f1\b0 \'a0The response to questions such as these will differ depending on the position being applied for. Answers will often revolve around: strategic decision-making,\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.walkme.com/glossary/change-leadership/?t=21&camp=adoption-blog"}}{\fldrslt leading change}}, implementation of digital initiatives, workforce training, and so forth.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
How do you manage change for employees?
\f1\b0 \'a0Digital transformation, by its very nature, involves\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://change.walkme.com/organizational-change-faq/?t=21&camp=adoption-blog"}}{\fldrslt organizational change}}. The implementation of digital technology is certainly important, but someone will have to manage employees\'92 expectations, their training, and so forth. Poorly managed change can increase employee resistance, which is why communication and people skills should be emphasized.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Please provide an example of the most successful digital initiative that you have led.
\f1\b0 \'a0Employers want to know how a candidate would react in certain circumstances, how they would deal with challenges, how they manage people, and how they approach decisions, and how these contributed to the candidate\'92s successful leadership. For that reason, it is useful to provide details about each of these areas: decision-making,\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.fool.com/the-blueprint/people-management/"}}{\fldrslt people management}}, challenges, and outcomes.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
How do you see technology evolving over the next ten years?
\f1\b0 \'a0Naturally, it is good to describe one\'92s own opinion on the matter. However, as with the other questions covered here, employers are most interested in their own welfare. It therefore pays to focus on how technology advances would impact the industry in question.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
What is the most influential digital technology in implementing digital transformation?
\f1\b0 \'a0Though many types of technology play a role in digital transformation, some are more foundational than others.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.investopedia.com/terms/d/data-analytics.asp"}}{\fldrslt Data analytics}}, for instance, are crucial for the modern business, and play a role in virtually every business function. Digital adoption platforms, which automate and streamline employee training, can also be applied in a wide range of digital transformation scenarios.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\sa520\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl500\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs32 \cf4 \cb3 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 1. How do you see technology evolving over the next decade?
\f3\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Social and digital change is inevitable, and business leaders have slowly understood that, and this question is an interviewer\'92s way of judging your views on the same. So, it is an excellent option to openly describe your opinion on this matter and show your industry knowledge.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 You can elaborate on the recent digital experiments that caught your attention and suggest ways to implement them into the recruiter\'92s company.\

\f2\b 2. What is the most important technology in a digital transformation project?
\f3\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Modern technologies like data analytics, digital marketing, and data science are some of the widely used processes while formulating digital transformation strategies. These processes help automate and streamline employment training programmes by introducing them to new digital products, suggesting ways to implement them, helping solve difficulties arising during use, and more.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 In addition to the ones mentioned above, you can add details on the modern technologies that you might have used in your previous organisation, the challenges you faced while implementing them, and how you overcame them.\

\f2\b 3. What challenges do you face while formulating digital transformation projects?
\f3\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 There can be an array of challenges a digital transformation professional faces regularly. Below, we list some of the common challenges professionals face in organisations:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl500\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 Higher Costs:
\f3\b0 \'a0Digital transformation projects are costlier than other business strategies. And arranging capital investment for digital transformation is one of the most significant challenges professional faces.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 Implementation Risks:
\f3\b0 \'a0There can be uncertainty surrounding the formulation and implementation of digital transformation projects because multiple modern technologies are used in the process. And each one of them can affect the outcome of the project.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 Time Constraints:
\f3\b0 \'a0Digital transformation projects have a lot of time constraints, making them difficult to complete on time, leading to missing deadlines and increasing costs.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 Additional Management:
\f3\b0 \'a0It is harder for organisations working with traditional structures to surmount digital transformation projects. It requires effectiveness, more patience, and long-term efforts to achieve desired results.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl500\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf4 \cb3 4. How would you ensure that a digital transformation project stays on track?
\f3\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 With this question, the interview tries to peek into your mindset and understand your process of setting up a digital transformation project. They also try to know how you perform under pressure.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 So, you can answer this question in the following way:\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 I would ensure that I have a detailed roadmap of the digital transformation project. It will help me analyse the progress of the project and closely monitor the plan and goals achieved in the project. I would also communicate this roadmap to key stakeholders and team members to avoid miscommunication.\

\f2\b 5. What is more important, according to you, being technologically fluent or excellent at working with people?
\f3\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 A digital transformation professional should be technically sound and good with people to tackle technical and people problems. This will allow them to achieve goals faster. Therefore, a perfect combination of a technologically strong and good communicator is ideal for surviving in the current business milieu riddled with uncertainties.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 1. What IS digital transformation to you?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Digital transformation is, in reality, a 2 phase process. The first part is about the usage of digital technologies like cloud computing and social networking. The second half, on the other hand, is concerned about changing how the organization works itself.\
They complement each other in reality. If you think the first as \'91what\'92, the second is certainly about \'91how\'92. You cannot succeed without taking into account both of them.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 2. Why do you think is digital transformation so important?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 There are many reasons behind the necessity of business transformation. One of the key reasons is that an organization has failed to evolve naturally over time. Another slightly different reason is the change in consumer behavior over time. Whatever may the reason be, if you think it is going to benefit the organization it becomes important.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 3. Is it equally important for all types of businesses?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Certainly not. Business to business industry, for example, is much more concerned about automation and cost reduction. So it all ultimately boils down to having an effective action plan.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 4. What are the most important elements of digital transformation?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 First, a clear vision \'96 absolutely necessary. Having a clear vision of what your organization NEEDS and what doesn\'92t is in fact key to success. You certainly don\'92t want to waste your resources on things that simply don\'92t matter. Second, a well-tested strategy. And last but not the least, the technology itself. Knowing what you want is not enough, after all \'96 you need to know how to achieve them.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 5. What could create additional value if the employees were working together more closely?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 An organization is not merely a machine, it\'92s a hierarchical social structure. There would be cases when an employee wouldn\'92t be able to make sense of the data. So pairing them with people who are using them could make a difference.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 6. Which functions, according to you, would yield more value if there were more coordination?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Working in small groups can work wonders. Pairing people who normally do not work together can have a remarkable outcome in terms of productivity. The team members start to see newer opportunities and experience the situation in a new light.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 7. How would/could you implement your action plan?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Collaboration is the key to any success. So keep testing your ideas. Share your ideas with others, maybe with someone from another team. Small experiments are a great way to break the ice.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 8. Where do you think the change is taking place?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 The start is always tough. You never know where exactly to start. The digital journey could be intimidating, and daunting at the same time. But as the spearhead of this transformation process, you need to understand the new frontiers where the changes are taking place. Moreover, you need to understand what aspects of the business are getting affected by it and what kind of foundation is needed to support that kind of transformation.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 9. Where should BUSINESSES start?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 It is one of the most common digital transformation leader interview questions that you would face. The starting point depends on the need of the specific organization. The goal ultimately is to optimize and coordinate resources more carefully. For some organizations, the top priority is to connect the internal resources more efficiently. For others, the coordination of internal operations is much more important.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 10. What are the main obstacles in your opinion?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 One of the main obstacles that the organizations face is the strategy \'96 a well-thought, battle-tested strategy. The actual obstacle is the lack of an informed strategic view of the whole situation. Another very common hindrance is the lack of joined-up thinking. Often you would see a plan that is all over the place, and the most probable reason behind such a mess is that the decision-takers have no idea as to what to expect from the new technology.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 11. How are you going to take the budget into account? What role does the budget play in your plan?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Many transformation journeys come to their knees soon after they start due to having a rigid budgetary cycle. Your plan needs to have the steam to achieve the long-term goal while taking into account the short-term milestones. Studies suggest even less than one-fifth of the organizations are able to quantify the return on investment.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 12. What do you think is a \'93digital business platform\'94?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 A digital business platform (DBP) is a recombination of a variety of different tools in a single package. These orchestration and integration tools enable the organization to create new assets.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 13. What is the need for an effective \'93digital business platform\'94?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 The need for a \'93digital business platform\'94 is multi-dimensional. But the key reason why an organization would need a DBP is simply the associated cost. Creating and maintaining the tools internally would be way too expensive, if also not time-consuming.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 14. What makes a \'91digital business platform\'92 better than the others? What differentiates them?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Speed to market and ongoing work agility is of top priority when it comes to choosing a good \'91digital business platform\'92. You would also like to know if the platform offers cloud-based service and good API service. While not essential these are critical to a pleasant and flexible user experience. Engagement is a good metric for gauging usability as it helps measure to which extent it provides appropriate user experience to a wide variety of workers.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf6 OPEN QUESTIONS ABOUT DIGITAL TRANSFORMATION
\f1\b0 \
These are the type of questions that have no right or wrong answers. They are asked simply to judge your knowledge as well as your thinking capabilities.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 15. How important do you think it is for the teams to collaborate across functions?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 The digital transformation journey is not a separate thread of execution. It is an organization-wide process. As an expert, you need to put emphasis on internal collaboration. No doubt, leaders put teams that integrate functions across the organization at a premium.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 16. Tell us how you have cultivated the RIGHT MINDSET to deliver the promise of the technology?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 This is a question designed to assess your strengths and weaknesses. The evaluator is trying to understand your mindset, how well you perform as a part of a team, how open are to new and novel ideas no matter where they are coming from, and obviously how well you can deliver the business value of a technology. Having the right mindset and an open attitude towards embracing changes is, in fact, the secret to success.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 17. How does communication take place inside an organization?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 Communication is an effective way of provoking new thoughts as well as encouraging new behaviors that can add value. So communicating and exchanging ideas with your colleagues and superiors can make the change. Communication is not limited to only having dialogues; they can come in many other formats. In a nutshell, you should be \'91listening for\'92 (some useful idea) rather than simply \'91listening to\'92.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 18. How can you leave your impression on the digital investments that can sustain value?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 It is a rather tricky question. There are certainly no wrong or right answers. The evaluator might be trying to get a hold of your thought process. They are trying to gauge how innovation played its part in your strategy.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 19. What do YOU need to do differently? What are the things that you would like to change about yourself?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 The feeling of \'91superiority\'92 is possibly the most common hindrance in learning something new. As soon as you start thinking that you know enough of it you are doomed. It has to be changed, sooner rather than later. In this fast-moving, ever-changing world you are simply going to fall behind if you do not keep learning.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 20. Tell us how you have helped an organization achieve the goal through digital transformation?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 A very important question. The evaluator is looking for certain aspects of the transformation in your answer. First, do the candidate even have the vision that is suitable for the company? Second, is he/she a leader material? Third, How much do you deserve the position? The following two questions are often followed by this question.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 21. What were the things that went according to the plans?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 This is very common among digital strategy interview questions and needs special attention. Try not to boast too much, while keeping the good parts intact. Needless to say, try to be as honest as possible. The scent of dishonesty can be tracked from miles afar.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 22. What did NOT go according to the plans?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 This is most probably even more vital than the earlier question. Never, ever say: \'93None!\'94 (yes, even if that was the case which is very unlikely). Get ready to be bombarded with a question like, \'93how would your plans be different if you were assigned the same task NOW?\'94.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 23. Where do you think the company would find itself after two or three years? How do you think the transformation is going to affect the organization?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 It can be a bit hard to answer. You cannot be too optimistic, else you would sound like you are being wishy-washy. That being said, you should not be too critical either. That might show that you are not confident about your plan of action. The best thing to do is to place a realistic-looking future plan, be it a bit on the conservative side.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf5 \strokec5 24. How would you make your strategy future-proof? Any opinion?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf6 \strokec6 The evaluator is probably looking for an honest answer. Really! Nobody knows about the future. Nobody knows how the events are going to turn out. So it would be better if you try to deliver your suggestions (no matter how hilarious they might sound) and mention that the future is uncertain.\
\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa200\partightenfactor0

